Simple Firefox Plugin Base
==========================

This is a repository which contains helper classes and utilities for bundling
directly with a Firefox plugin.


Classes
-------

The following classes are provided, for more information see the source files
directly, they are documented.

### CSSBuilder

A simple utility which allows to build CSS styles in an object/function
oriented manner.

### DynamicStyleSheets

A helper class which allows to register and removed stylesheets.

### Preferences

A wrapper around the Preferences service provided by Firefox which provides
many methods.

### ResourceAlias

A utility which allows to load resources.

### StyleSheet

A helper class which works similar to DynamicStyleSheets, but allows to register
multiple stylesheets as one big one.

